overview: Heavy metal band Iron Maiden's 2008 Somewhere Back in Time World Tour. This concert recording accompanies the documentary film "Iron Maiden: Flight 666". The 16 songs performed were filmed live in 16 different cities giving you the full experience of the live power of Maiden and their fans all around the globe.
tagline: Somewhere Back in Time World Tour 2008
title: Iron Maiden - Flight 666 - The Concert
